item.title: CVE-2022-40602|2024-08-03T12:21:46.528Z -- zyxel -- lte3301-m209
item.description: A flaw in the Zyxel LTE3301-M209 firmware verisons prior to V1.00(ABLG.6)C0 could allow a remote attacker to access the device using an improper pre-configured password if the remote administration feature has been enabled by an authenticated administrator.
